Fix two bugs in @tmustier/pi-agent-teams (v0.1.2):

1. Windows: worker subprocess spawn ENOENT
   teammate-rpc.ts -> add shell: process.platform === "win32"

2. Worker stalls after first task — second task never triggers agent_start
   worker.ts -> agent_end no longer calls sendUserMessage inside event handler;
   dequeued to poll loop which calls maybeStartNextWork() from outside any handler.

